datatypes.recordtypes

Class SzoliRekord

  • java.lang.Object
    • datatypes.recordtypes.Record
      • datatypes.recordtypes.SzoliRekord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class SzoliRekord
extends Record
implements java.io.Serializable
    The record type for solarium service it also implements the interface serializable and extends the class Record It has all the attributes needed to properly record a solarium service purchase.
